text: Abbie Cornish (born 7 August 1982) is an Australian actress who has performed in some notable movies. Cornish was born in New South Wales, and grew up on a farm. Her movies include Somersault, Candy and Bright Star. She played Emma Matisse in One Perfect Day. She plays Ellen Murphy in the 2014 remake of RoboCop. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Australian movie actors Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from New South Wales
